0 minutes.  And dropped the map every time.  Hence six kills, six happy Rangers.<P>The sword received for this quest is the Short Sowrd of Morin.  It's stats are dmg 6, dly 22, wht 3.  +3 agi, +3 str.  I'm not 100% sure on the weight or delay, this is from memory.<P>Go join a party in West Karana and have fun. Just make sure your not all in your early 20s.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#D9DCE8"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana">Band</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana">Hi<BR>Could you tell me which NPC gives the quest? and what else is needed (For Sword)<P>Also I have the Named Cyclops Charm (Neclace) what else do i need for that ramger quest, and who is the NPC?<P>THanks<P>Band<P></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#E8EAF0"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana">Kaisan</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana">The NPCs you need to speak to are at the Ranger's settlement in Kithicor Forest.<P>Morin <insert surname here> issues the sword quest.  You only need the map from the ghoul messager for this quest.<P>Gandari issues the armour quests.  Multiple items are required for the different pieces armour.</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE></td></tr></table> 
